thread.title_full: Compare Travel Insurance reviewed by Customer

author: Customer
title: Customer
text: This is a great site to use to be able to easily compare a wide range of travel insurers. Although the 'Choice' recommendations for insureres were not there, many others were. This made it easy to compare costs and benefits without having to do the searching for the insurers one by one.
